description: With the Dominican Festival taking place in Santiago R.R., we're smoking Dominican Cigars today; C.O. JONES by Joche Blanco (Las Palmas) and Topper Cigars, We celebrate George Washington's birthday (what's up with the car sales?), hit the mail bag, 99 problems but a cigar ain't one, cigars and sexism and whole lot more!
